# System architecture

Design as **separate services/modules** with clear separation of concerns. Avoid monolithic files.

## Required conceptual modules

| Module | Responsibility |
|--------|------------------|
| **Orchestrator** | Task manager; routes work to agents |
| **Web Automation Agent** | Playwright-based browser tasks |
| **Voice Agent** | Vapi (fallback: Twilio) for real calls |
| **Slack Interface** | Commands, async replies, approvals |
| **Context Store** | User/session data |
| **Task State Manager** | Status and lifecycle (persisted) |
| **Approval System** | Human-in-the-loop gates |
| **Logging & Observability** | Timestamped actions, traces, debuggability |

New code should map to these boundaries unless the user specifies a different structure.
